(65, 'Achivements', '<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Institute of Engineering and Rural Technology started its Engineering Degree Division in 2001. In just a few years the Engineering Degree Division has achieved a lot under the guidance of its administration, teachers and hard work of the students. I.E.R.T\\''s name has become synonymous with quality technical education as can be seen through the results of its students.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Some of the major achievements are:</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;On the basis of the overall third year result of the 2004 batch I.E.R.T has achieved third rank among all the institutes of U.P.</span></p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\r\\n<ul style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\\" type=\\"disc\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Nidhi Tiwari&nbsp;</span>of electronics engineering Branch secured<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;4th rank</span>&nbsp;in the U.P.Technical University in the academic year of 2002.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Stuti Sahai</span>&nbsp;of electronics engineering Branch secured<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;8th rank</span>&nbsp;in the U.P.Technical University in the academic year of 2003.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Ankit Verma</span>&nbsp;belonging to Electronics Branch scored 1603 in the academic year of 2004 for an overall percentage of 80.1% in the third year. He is at&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">third</span>&nbsp;position in merit list of U.P Technical University.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Praveen Dwivedi</span>&nbsp;of Computer Science &amp; Engineering&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">topped&nbsp;</span>the merit list as declared by the U.P.T.U, Lucknow in 2005.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\">Six of our Computer Science &amp; Engineering student have secured&Acirc; position among the top ten student as declared by the U.P.T.U Lucknow in 2005.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Prashant Pathak</span>&nbsp;of final year scored 97.8 percentile in CAT 2005.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Rishi Raj</span>&nbsp;of final year scored 97.3 percentile in CAT 2005 &amp; got admission in&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Symbosis Pune.</span></li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Vidya Shankar&nbsp;</span>belonging to Industrial &amp; Production Branch of final year scored<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;368</span>&nbsp;A.I.R rank in&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">GATE</span>examination 2006 and is in I.I.T Delhi.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Gautam Ghosh&nbsp;</span>belonging to Electronics Branch of third year scored<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;482</span>&nbsp;A.I.R rank in<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">&nbsp;GATE</span>&nbsp;examination 2006.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\" type=\\"disc\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">More than 10</span>&nbsp;student got good A.I.R rannks in&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">GATE&nbsp;</span>2006.</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">The Institute also stood 1st in the second merit list of Engineering Institutes all over the country in&nbsp;<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">GATE</span>&nbsp;result of 2004 as per the data provided by I.I.T Delhi.</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n</div>', 'achivements'),
(66, 'Life at IERT', '<p><span style=\\"color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">Under construction</span></p>', 'life_iert'),
(67, 'Technovation', '<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Technovation is the Institute\\''s annual technical festival. Technovation is conducted by the student community of IERT and promotes the development and honing of scientific and entrepreneurial skills in the students. It is organized in first week of April. Altogether over 30 events take place under the following categories: CYBERTRON, ELEKTRON, MECHATRON, ROBOTRON, BRAINFORMERS, PAPERTRON,&nbsp;CANVASS, NON-TRON and X-FIRE. Students from various colleges in and around Allahabad participate in the event.&nbsp;<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" /><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />One of the most popular events WAR OF BANDS is organized in the campus, where numerous bands from different institutions participate and thrill the audience. It is a massive success and a crowd of over thousand students form the audience.&nbsp;<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />Another addition to the list of events was the Kavi Sammelan, KAVYANICAL which attracted poets from various cities.<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />On the last day of Technovation, a blood donation camp is organized in which students from diverse background come forward and contribute to the cause.<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />The tech-fest is concluded with the Prize Distribution Ceremony by an eminent personality.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\"><u style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\">Event Organization</u></span><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">:&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Technovation is organized and conducted by 3rd year students of the institute.<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />The Technovation Committee is 3-tiered:<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />Heading the team is the Head Coordinator along with a team of Managers (Core Committee) subdivided according to their departments.&nbsp;<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />For smooth functioning, certain portfolios are allotted to every manager. The portfolios can be broadly categorized into two sections - Administration and Events. The administrative portfolios primarily include tasks like Accounts, Infrastructure, Marketing, Hospitality, Publicity and Media. The events portfolios include responsibility for each of the numerous events in Technovation each year.&nbsp;<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />Each manager then has his own team of organizers. The organizers help the manager in looking into the finer details of the portfolio allotted and ensuring that it is executed smoothly.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\"><u style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\">Events and Website management</u></span><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">:</span></p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Technovation, the annual tech-fest&nbsp;of the institute, comprises of over 30 events, four to five events per department. It also hosts online events in which students from all over the country participate. All the details regarding it can be obtained from the Official Technovation Website.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />Major events-</p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\r\\n<ul style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Code Trap</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">C Champ</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">War Of Bands</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Robotics&nbsp;</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<div style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">&nbsp;</div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">The official website of the technovation is designed and maintained by the students of the WebTeam of the Institute.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" /><span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\"><u style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\">Prize Distribution:&nbsp;</u></span><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />Each event has an attractive cash prize and/or gift coupons from sponsors.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">&nbsp;</p>', 'technovation'),
(68, 'Sports', '<p><span style=\\"color: #444444; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">Sports and cultural activities are essential part of any education institute. They provide the basis for building up team spirit and inoculate a feeling of sportsmanship in the individual. Sports and Games are also essential to build healthy body, which is essential for a healthy mind. The Institute hosts outdoor sports like Cricket, Football, Volleyball and Tennis as well as indoor games like Table-Tennis, Badminton, Chess and Carrom. The Inter-Branch Cricket Tournament is a major highlight and highly anticipated.</span><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #444444; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" /><span style=\\"color: #444444; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">&ldquo;Health is Wealth&rdquo;. Keeping this in mind, the institute organizes numerous healthy and creative, cultural and sports activities. This helps the students to show their talents and encourage all round development of their personalities. The Institute organizes an Annual Sports meet to explore the talents of the students in athletics, outdoor and indoor games. The students actively participate in other inter-college, inter-university and inter-state competitions.</span></p>', 'sports'),
(69, 'Udbhav', '<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Udbhav, is the annual cultural festival of the Institute of Engineering and Rural Technology. It is held for 3 days in last week of October every year, to celebrate the Institute&rsquo;s Engineering Degree Division Foundation Day.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">The function comprises of Chief Guest&rsquo;s speech, a vast range of musical and cultural events and competitions, informal events which show cases professional performances along with the college&rsquo;s annual progress report in academics and curricular activities, followed by the prize distribution ceremony in the field of academics, sports and the other successful students who are rewarded for their contribution to the Institute.<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" />The competitions include:</p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\r\\n<ul style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\\">\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Dance</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Music (Solo and Duet)</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Drama</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Humorous skits</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Quiz</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Fine Arts ( Drawing and Painting )</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Face Painting</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Antakshari</li>\\r\\n<li style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 5px;\\">Fashion show, etc.</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">These are competitions of Udbhav that provide an opportunity to the young enthusiastic participants to live their passion and make their dreams come true. The cultural festival is concluded with the Director&rsquo;s inspiring speech to encourage students to do well in future.</p>', 'udbhav'),
(70, 'Freshers Function', '<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Fresher function is organized to welcome the new students, who had just become the part of institution by the batch prior to them. Both the faculty members and the older students of the institute promise the new student for their bright future. The function plays an important role in the interaction of new student with their seniors.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">A vast range of musical and cultural events provide a platform to the new student to explore their hidden talents and learn the sharp skills.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">The main attraction of the function is the Mr. and Ms. Fresher contest and many other consolation prizes are to be won.</p>', 'freshers'),
(71, 'Farewell', '<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">The function begins with full enthusiasm by the members of pre final year and a mixture of obsession and hope among departing ones.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">Event starts with the Director\\''s address and after colorful programs inundated with cultural talents of students function come to most waited humorous title distribution ceremony.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;\\" align=\\"justify\\">The function comes to end by rewards of best seniors viewed by their juniors throughout the course</p>', 'farewell'),
(72, 'TPO cell', '<div class=\\"course-wrapper col-md-8 col-sm-7\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 780px; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">\\r\\n<article class=\\"course-item\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"page-row\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 30px;\\">\\" Dreams are not those which come while asleep, they are ones which do not let be asleep\\".s IERT has always been well spring of compeititive technical minds who have spread their enlightening potentials round the globe.The spirit of conquering every hurdle hgas been intensified year after year.The journey of being mere stones to sparkling diamonds has been well worked out of studentsby the constant effort put in by the TPO cell.The rigorous hard work by the members as team has long proven to be an asset to college We are proud to have created a niche of placements.\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444;\\">The Training and Placement Cell of the Institute is headed by members of tpo cell. It consists of student members from all the branches who help in coordinating in certain aspects of placement. The cell maintains complete information about each student of the Institute and is responsible for maintaining links with various organizations.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444;\\">Numerous companies visit IERT each year to offer jobs to the students. Some students also participate in pool campus placements for job opportunities. Some of the leading companies where our students have taken up job offers:</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444;\\">Accenture, Infosys, Satyam, TCS, Wipro, HCL, BirlaSoft, Zuari cement, Indorama, Syntel, Mahindra &amp; Mahindra, Escorts, L&amp;T InfoTech and many more.</p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444;\\" align=\\"justify\\">&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n</article>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<aside class=\\"page-sidebar  col-md-3 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 292.5px; margin-left: 97.5px; color: #333333; font-family: \\''Helvetica Neue\\'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;\\">\\r\\n<section class=\\"links\\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 30px; background: #f5f5f5;\\"></section>\\r\\n</aside>', 'tpo'),
